Matt King (comedian) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matt_King_(comedian) 0 Matt King (born 31 January 1968) is an English actor, DJ and comedian. He is most known for his role as Super Hans in the British sitcom Peep Show. Matt_King ( born_31_January_1968 ) is an_English_actor , DJ_and_comedian .
